channel.title: New 317 server. Edgeville Supremacy! (videos & pics)
channel.description:
I know I'm not known at all on this forum. But this is a new server, it's been online for about a month now. (5.31.12.)
We average about 5-8 players on a day, and we need moar! haha.
We have a webclient. here's the link: www.edgevillesupremacy.webatu.com
Forums: www.edgevillesupremacy.createaforum.com
We have a youtube account as well, 2 videos a day at least. www.youtube.com/rspsEdgeville
Here's some pics:
Thieving Stalls! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/ThievingStalls.png[/img]
Player Killing Teleport! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Teleports.png[/img]
Stores! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Stores.png[/img]
Slayer Tower! Get slayer tasks from Vannaka at home by the stalls! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Slayer.png[/img]
Skilling Area & Stores! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Skiller.png[/img]
100% Operational Fight Pits! Rewards if you win! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Pits.png[/img]
Pest Control! 100% Operational! Two pics to show you! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/PestControl.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Pestcontrol2.png[/img]
Newbie Training Area! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Monster.png[/img]
Minigame Teleports! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Minigameteles.png[/img]
Island Training Area! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Island.png[/img]
GodWars! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Godwar.png[/img]
Donator Island & Donator Store! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Donator.png[/img]
Daggonath Lair! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/dagg.png[/img]
Axe Killing Custom Minigame! At what looks like a bunch of Accumulators, kill them, get points for awesome rewards! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Customgame.png[/img]
Rock Crabs Training Area! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Crabs.png[/img]
Cave Training Area! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Cave.png[/img]
100% Working Barrows! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Barrows.png[/img]
Assault Minigame and Shop! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/Assault.png[/img] WORKING CLAWS SPEC [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/CLAWS.png[/img]
WORKING BGS SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/BGSSPEC.png[/img]
WORKING AGS SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/AGSSPEC.png[/img]
WORKING ZGS SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/ZGS.png[/img]
WORKING VESTA LONG SWORD WITH SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/VLS.png[/img]
WORKING STATIUS! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/STAIUS.png[/img]
WORKING SGS SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/SGSSPEC.png[/img]
DRAGON SCIMITAR SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/SCIM.png[/img]
WORKING DRAGON MACE SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/mace.png[/img]
WORKING DRAGON HALBERD SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/DRAGONHALBERD.png[/img]
WORKING D LONG SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/DLONG.png[/img]
WORKING DDS SPEC! [IMG]http://i1260.photobucket.com/albums/ii563/Denode7/DDSSPEC1.png[/img]
Hope to see you all!
